                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d377">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_HHL1">Hopkins</persName> Papers</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">
                        <persName corresp="#p_HHL1">Hopkins</persName> Notes</hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d377fn1">These notes, in <persName corresp="#p_HHL1"
                            >Hopkins</persName>’ handwriting, are headed “Mr. <persName
                            corresp="#p_EA1">Eden</persName>[’s] report of Foreign Minister
                        Committee”. The material reproduced here ends at the middle of a page and
                        appears to be incomplete. No other <persName corresp="#p_HHL1"
                            >Hopkins</persName> notes of this meeting have been found.</note>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-chapter-heading" calendar="gregorian"
                        when="1943-12-01T13:00:00+03:25">December 1, 1943, 1 p.m.</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>1. Turkey should be asked to come into the war &amp; invite President of Turkey
                    to come to Cairo to meet the President of U. S. A. &amp; Prime Minister.</p>
                <p>Mr. <persName corresp="#p_EA1">Eden</persName> asked <persName corresp="#p_MGC1"
                        >Marshall</persName> [<hi rend="italic">Marshal</hi>] <persName
                        corresp="#p_SIV1">Stalin</persName> whether the Soviet Government wished to
                    send a representative—if so he would of course be welcomed.</p>
                <p>M. <persName corresp="#p_SIV1">Stalin</persName> answered that he would send such
                    a representative.</p>
                <p>Proposed telegram to Pres. <persName corresp="#p_II1">Inonu</persName> was
                    presented and discussed.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
